items.text: full outside off, tapped off the front foot to wide long off. They walk across for the single
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, 1 run

items.text: full outside off, driven down the ground but mistimed. Stopped by Shakib on his folow through
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: back of a length outside off, stays low as Raza backs away and muscles this in front of square. Can't beat the man at cover
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: how did that miss leg stump? Full on off stump, and stays very low! Tries to defend but the ball takes the inside edge and slips through between his bat and pad. Goes just past leg stump. Well bowled
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Sikandar Raza, 2 runs

items.text: back of a length on middle and this time Shakib's been sent away! Goes deep into the crease and pulls with a lot of power over cow corner
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Sikandar Raza, SIX runs

items.text: full outside off, floated in but well negated off the front foot. Defended
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: full outside off once again, defended back to Sunzamul
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: full, but slightly wider outside off, driven with the bat's open face to point
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: short outside off, cut away despite the ball angling into him. Goes past point, forcing the man in the deep to cut it off
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, 2 runs

items.text: full on middle stump, nudged off the front foot towards midwicket. No one there, forcing the bowler to chase behind it
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, 1 run

items.text: full on middle and leg, tapped with soft hands towards the leg side
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: good length on middle stump, steps back and punches off the back foot. Straight to mid on
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, no run

items.text: overpitched outside off, driven well off the front foot to deep extra cover
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Moor, 1 run

items.text: back of a length outside off, backs away and tries to cut. But not hit well enough, and doesn't have the direction either. Straight to short cover
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: full outside off, forces Raza to step forward and tackle the delivery. Defended off the front foot
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: full outside off, big stride forward and fended with soft hands
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: back of a length outside off, steps towards the leg side and makes a little extra room. Cut uppishly past point to the man in the deep
items.shortText: Shakib Al Hasan to Sikandar Raza, 1 run

items.preText: Naseer: "Sikandar Raza is my favorite player. He is a calm person, I hope he will make a 50" -- The rest of Zimbabwe would hope so too, I suppose. Only the tail after this.
items.text: good length outside off, tapped down the ground to long off
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Sikandar Raza, 1 run

items.text: full ball on off stump, no real spin. Defended with soft hands
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: full on off stump, drives straight but takes the inside edge. Flies away towards square leg
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: full outside off again, defended with the bat's open face to cover point
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.text: tossed up on middle, and he attempts a slog sweep! Big wind up from the batsman, but a blind slog, really. Flies over first slip's head. Lucky
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, 2 runs

items.text: full outside off, tapped down the ground back to the bowler. Sunzamul finishes his ten overs (1 for 29)
items.shortText: Sunzamul Islam to Moor, no run

items.preText: Fizz returns. Five more overs for him to go. Twenty five dot balls in his first 30 balls.
items.text: back of a length outside off, angles further away from the batsman. Raza shoulders his arms
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Sikandar Raza, no run

items.text: full on leg stump, gentle offcutter, defended with soft hands back towards the non-striker
items.shortText: Mustafizur Rahman to Sikandar Raza, no run
